mpauth.py

mod_python library cribbed from mpopenid.py
Apache form-based authentication using mod_python.
Requires python 2.4 or higher, mod_python, and
the ipaddr.py library from Google.

Access granted either by username and password,
or with the allow-from option that whitelists
network subnets. 

To use, replace is_authentic method with a real
database, .htpasswd, or ldap lookup or other
way to verify user.